scrabble.localization

Class AlphabetDistributionSuper_en

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.ResourceBundle
      • java.util.ListResourceBundle
        • scrabble.localization.AlphabetDistributionSuper_en

  • public class AlphabetDistributionSuper_en
extends java.util.ListResourceBundle
    Bundle class that holds the amound of each letter in the bag. Greek version. (FOR SUPER SCRABBLE) The capital letter is used as the key and the returned string is the number it in the bag.
    In order to create a full localization for the game, you will need to create
    Localization_**.java, Alphabet_**.java, AlphabetPoints_**.java and AlphabetDistribution_**.java
    classes, where "**" represents the country code.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    George Piskas
